Privacy Policy
Introduction
Play 25 values your privacy. This privacy policy outlines how we handle your information when you use our app.
Data Collection and Use
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information, including but not limited to names, email addresses, phone numbers, or other identifiable information.
Third-Party Services
Our app does not integrate with third-party services that collect or process user data.
Cookies and Tracking
Our app does not use cookies or other tracking technologies.
Children’s Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect information from children under the age of 13. Since no data is collected, there are no concerns regarding children’s privacy.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be posted here, and we recommend reviewing this page periodically.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at support@play25online.com.
Cookie Use
We use cookies to ensure a smooth browsing experience.  By continuing we assume you accept the use of cookies.
